@notice remove 'user' from the user list of a contract 'self'.

@notice msg sender removes itself from the sponsor candidates list of contract 'self'.

params.blockNumber: balance will be calculated at blockNumber
params.self: account address which may be contract account or external account address.

returns._0: self the amount of VET at blockNumber

params.blockNumber: energy will be calculated at blockNumber
params.self: account address which may be contract account or external account address.

returns._0: the amount of energy at blockNumber

params.newMaster: new master account which will be set.

returns._0: value indexed by key at self storage

addUser(address,address).notice: add address 'user' to the user list of a contract 'self'.

currentSponsor(address).notice: return current selected sponsor of contract 'self'

isSponsor(address,address).notice: check if 'sponsorAddress' is the sponser of contract 'self'.

isUser(address,address).notice: check if address 'user' is the user of contract 'self'.

removeUser(address,address).notice: remove 'user' from the user list of a contract 'self'.

selectSponsor(address,address).notice: select 'sponsorAddress' to be current selected sponsor of contract 'self'

setMaster(address,address).notice: 'newMaster' will be set to contract 'self' and this function only works when msg sender is the old master.

sponsor(address).notice: msg sender volunteers to be a sponsor of the contract 'self'.

unsponsor(address).notice: msg sender removes itself from the sponsor candidates list of contract 'self'.

userCredit(address,address).notice: return the current credit of 'user' of the contract 'self'.
